{"author":"RebarBotNava","data":{"alias":"floral-glutinous-cob","description":"## Why\n`test_leaves_registry_coverage.py::test_every_leaf_has_real_body` defines \"real body\" as\n>=3 AST statements OR a regex match for effect-shaped tokens (`client.`, `.append`,\n`subprocess.run`, ...) over `inspect.getsource` (`:83-100`). It can pass while a leaf sends\nthe wrong target, drops a field, returns the wrong follow-on, or swallows a required error.\nVALIDATED.\n\n## What\nParameterize every leaf in `_LEAVES` and assert its observable effect with a mock Jira\nclient: the exact client/store call, returned `ApplyResult`, follow-ons, and failure\nbehavior.\n\n## Scope\n- `tests/unit/rebar_reconciler/orchestrate/test_leaves_registry_coverage.py` (or a new\n  per-leaf test module); may keep the AST heuristic as an explicitly-supplemental guard.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] Each registry leaf has a behavioral test asserting its expected external effect.\n- [ ] A leaf that targets the wrong entity / drops a field / returns the wrong follow-on\n      fails its test.\n- [ ] If the AST heuristic is retained, it is relabeled as a supplemental structural guard,\n      not behavioral coverage.\n- [ ] `make test` green.","id":"eba0-91bb-c2d2-433e","parent_id":"bf50-2131-271b-4fdc","priority":3,"tags":["p2","reconciler","change-detector"],"ticket_type":"story","title":"Replace leaf-registry 'real body' heuristic with a per-leaf effect matrix"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1783784821714812001,"uuid":"ee2ed6f0-ee2e-4176-80ee-618afd66a33e"}